            = f.label :adless, "Eメールアドレス", class: "signup_body_main_format_addless_title_main"
            %br
            = f.label :addless, "(ZOZO ID)", class: "signup_body_main_format_addless_title_sub"
          .signup_body_main_format_addless_form
            = f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "Emeil", class: "signup_body_main_format_addless_form_main", placeholder: '例 :zozo@zozotown.jp'
            %br.signup_body_main_format_addless_form_sub ※ メールアドレスがZOZO IDとなります
            %br.signup_body_main_format_addless_form_checkbox セールやクーポンのお得な情報を受け取る
